### Send Confirmation Email
POST http://localhost:8081/send/confirmation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "to": "user@example.com",
  "subject": "Email Confirmation",
  "name": "John Doe",
  "confirmationLink": "https://example.com/confirm?token=abc123"
}

